  * Fix Maintainer field.
    - Also set distribution in debian/rules to Ubuntu-PPA so Maintainer doesn't
      get overridden.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 3.8.4.
  * Correctly depend on and suggest related packages.
    - Specifically Tk for Idle and Tk and GDBM debug packages.
  * Build GDBM and Tk from this package.

